task.summary: [MONDRIAN-1891] Removing some Java 7 only features so mongolap can compile and run correctly in Java 6.
[MONDRIAN-1891] Removing some Java 7 only features so mongolap can compile and run correctly in Java 6.

[ANALYZER-2413] Analyzer throws stack traces when NULLs or missing attributes are encountered in MongoDB collections
Correcting a remaining NPE that could be thrown when a null attribute is a part of a compound key. Also moved 2 tests out of SimpleQueryTest and into BasicQueryTest. SimpleQueryArrayTest runs all of the tests from SimpleQueryTest, which caused these two to fail, since they used the [Store Size in SQFT] attribute (not present in the array based cube)

[ANALYZER-2443] First pass of refactoring pentaho-mongodb-plugin to be a common library.
This pass removed all kettle related dependencies and kettle-specific features. 1) VariableSpace and MongoDbMeta were replaced with a simple properties collection. 2) LogChannelInterface usage was replaced with MongoUtilLogger interface, allowing clients to pass in a log handler of their choosing. 3) Utility methods .isEmpty and .cleansePath moved into a Util class. 4) Removed handling of kettle type conversion 5) Removed (at least for now) the ArrayExpansion class. 6) Created an empty stub for message handling to sit in place of the di class BaseMessages.
Many TODO items to be cleaned up.

[ANALYZER-2443] First pass of refactoring pentaho-mongodb-plugin to be a common library.

Many TODO items to be cleaned up.
[ANALYZER-2443] Implemented methods to retrieve messages from messages.properties.
[ANALYZER-2443] Introduced a functional test which exercises the UsernamePasswordMongoClientWrapper.
[ANALYZER-2443] Removed code unrelated to Mongo connections.
[ANALYZER-2442] Added idea project files. Also commented out publish of non-existent ".plain" artifact pending decision on obfuscation.
